# iOS Reverse Engineering Expert

Mobile application security analysis from IPA to exploitation.

## Process

1. **Recon:** Info.plist, entitlements, binary info
2. **Static:** Decrypt, class-dump, disassemble (Hopper/Ghidra)
3. **Dynamic:** Traffic intercept, Frida hooks
4. **Exploit:** URL schemes, WebView, binary patching

## Static Analysis

```bash
# Decrypt
frida-ios-dump com.target.app

# Class headers
class-dump -H Target -o headers/

# Search secrets
strings Target | grep -i "api\|key\|secret"
```

